<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>InnovaMind - Capacitación Técnica Retail</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <style>
        body { background-color: #f4f6f9; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; }
        .navbar-custom { background-color: #0d6efd; color: white; }
        .card-course { border: none; border-radius: 12px; transition: transform 0.2s; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        .card-course:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); }
        .badge-data { background-color: #e3f2fd; color: #0d6efd; font-weight: 600; }
        .offline-banner { background-color: #e6f4ea; color: #137333; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500; display: none; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-custom sticky-top shadow-sm">
        <div class="container d-flex justify-content-between align-content-center">
            <span class="navbar-brand mb-0 h1 text-white fw-bold"><i class="bi bi-brain-fill me-2"></i>InnovaMind</span>
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                <span class="badge bg-warning text-dark me-3"><i class="bi bi-trophy-fill me-1"></i> Sucursal Alborada: #2</span>
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1534528741775-53994a69daeb?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=100" class="rounded-circle" width="35" height="35" alt="Avatar">
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div id="offlineBanner" class="offline-banner text-center py-2 border-bottom">
        <i class="bi bi-cloud-arrow-down-fill me-2"></i> Modo de ultra-ahorro activo. Lecciones descargadas listas para reproducir sin internet.
    </div>

    <div class="container my-4" style="max-width: 600px;">
        <div class="mb-4 text-center text-sm-start">
            <h4 class="fw-bold mb-1">¡Hola, Andrea! 👋</h4>
            <p class="text-muted small">Módulo operativo: Retail & Distribución (Ecuador 2026)</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-3 mb-4 shadow-sm border-0 bg-white">
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                <div>
                    <h6 class="mb-1 fw-bold"><i class="bi bi-lightning-charge-fill text-warning me-1"></i> Ahorro de Datos Móviles</h6>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-0" style="font-size: 0.8rem;">Comprime videos a 3MB por lección para planes prepago.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="form-check form-switch">
                    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" role="switch" id="dataSaverSwitch" onchange="toggleDataSaver()">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card p-3 mb-4 shadow-sm border-0 bg-white">
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-2">
                <span class="fw-bold text-secondary small">Meta Semanal de la Sucursal</span>
                <span class="fw-bold text-primary small">75%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="progress" style="height: 10px;">
                <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped progress-bar-animated bg-success" role="progressbar" style="width: 75%"></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h6 class="fw-bold mb-3 text-secondary text-uppercase" style="font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 1px;">Tus Micro-Lecciones del Día (5 min)</h6>
        
        <div class="card card-course p-3 mb-3 bg-white">
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start mb-2">
                <span class="badge badge-data px-2 py-1"><i class="bi bi-phone me-1"></i> 2.8 MB</span>
                <span class="badge bg-success-subtle text-success border border-success-subtle">Recomendado</span>
            </div>
            <h6 class="fw-bold mb-1">Control Automatizado de Inventarios en Percha</h6>
            <p class="text-muted small mb-3">Aprende a registrar mermas en tiempo real usando la app de la tienda.</p>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                <span class="text-muted small"><i class="bi bi-clock me-1"></i> 3 min de video</span>
                <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm px-3 fw-bold" onclick="alert('Iniciando reproducción comprimida de 3 minutos...')">Iniciar lección</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card card-course p-3 mb-3 bg-white">
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-start mb-2">
                <span class="badge badge-data px-2 py-1"><i class="bi bi-phone me-1"></i> 3.1 MB</span>
                <span class="badge bg-secondary-subtle text-secondary border border-secondary-subtle">Pendiente</span>
            </div>
            <h6 class="fw-bold mb-1">Prevención de Pérdidas y Cuadrado Base de Caja</h6>
            <p class="text-muted small mb-3">Estrategias prácticas bajo la normativa comercial del mercado local.</p>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                <span class="text-muted small"><i class="bi bi-clock me-1"></i> 4 min de video</span>
                <button class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm px-3 fw-bold" onclick="alert('Cargando trivia interactiva...')">Iniciar lección</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function toggleDataSaver() {
            var checkBox = document.getElementById("dataSaverSwitch");
            var banner = document.getElementById("offlineBanner");
            if (checkBox.checked == true){
                banner.style.display = "block";
            } else {
                banner.style.display = "none";
            }
        }
    </script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
